						  Micro Edition (Java ME) <br>
						    Executive Committee                          
						  <br>&nbsp;<br>
						  <a href="#rizzo">Aplix, John Rizzo</a><br>
						  <a href="#olsson">Ericsson AB, Magnus Olsson</a><br>
						    <A href="#rogalski">IBM, Mark Rogalski</a><br>
						      <A href="#milikich">Motorola, Mike Milikich</a><br>
						      <a href="#savolainen">Nokia, Pentti Savolainen </a><br>
						      <a href="#lucas">Orange, Philippe Lucas</a><br>
						    <a href="#piesing">Philips, Jon Piesing</a><br>
